<LP>
   JOHNSTOWN, Pa. -- Bethlehem Steel Corp. said it intends to
offer to sell its Johnstown Freight Car Division. The steel
company said its decision was in keeping with its previously
stated policy of divesting assets not directly related to its
core steel business.
